high_descs: Grab a coffee cup from the counter
Put the coffee cup in the microwave
Take the cup from the microwave and take it to the shelf and put it up
anns.task_desc: Drying the coffee cup and putting it away

high_descs: Turn right, move around the island to the right, go to the microwave left of the fridge.
Pick up the mug on the counter next to the microwave.
Bring the mug to the microwave.
Heat the mug in the microwave.
Take the heated mug across the room to the wooden rack in the opposite corner.
Put the heated mug on the middle wooden rack.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated mug on the middle rack.

high_descs: Turn right, walk straight, turn right, walk to the microwave
Grab the white cup by the microwave
Step back, face the microwave on the counter
Open the microwave, put the cup in the microwave, close the microwave, heat the cup, open the microwave, take the cup out, close the microwave
Turn around, walk straight, turn left, walk to shelf at the end
Put the cup on the second shelf
anns.task_desc: Heat the cup with microwave, put the cup on the shelf
